A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a frustrated father sitting at a cluttered kitchen table surrounded by scattered game cards, coins, and an old rotary phone, while two excited young boys in the background eagerly hover near a glowing desktop computer displaying a fantasy game with dragons and castles. The scene is rendered in warm, muted retro colors with halftone dot textures, depicting the clash between old-world parental responsibilities and new digital entertainment. The father holds his head in one hand while the other gestures helplessly at a towering stack of paperwork and receipts. A piggy bank sits cracked open on the table, gold coins spilling out toward the computer's direction.
